abstract: College Basketball Roundup; University of Iowa men's basketball team defeats Rutgers, 90-76; other men's and women's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Peter Jok, the Big Ten’s reigning player of the week, led No. 9 Iowa to a tough victory over a pesky Rutgers team.
